<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/485775-hey-guys-are-all-the-books-heavily">Hey guys, are all the books heavily connected? I can only find the first part and the third in my city. So if I read the first one and not the other ones, would iI be missing a lot?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_485775'><a id="like_count_community_question_485775" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/485775?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F887877.Red_Seas_Under_Red_Skies">like</a></span>

