<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/902715.Before_They_Are_Hanged"><img alt="Before They Are Hanged (The First Law, #2)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1179318094l/902715._SX98_.jpg" />
